		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# üå± SPRING MARKETING NEWS ‚Äî Tech Stack\n**Live:** spring-marketing-news.vercel.app ¬∑ **Repo:** github.com/Farveblind5000/spring-marketing-news ¬∑ **Maj 2026**","x":-1300,"y":-1500,"width":2600,"height":140},
		{"id":"comp-savebutton","type":"text","text":"### SaveButton\n`app/components/SaveButton.tsx`\nBookmark-toggle ¬∑ skriver direkte til `user_saves` med browser-client","x":-1260,"y":-670,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"comp-genbutton","type":"text","text":"### GenerateDigestButton\n`app/components/GenerateDigestButton.tsx`\nKalder `/api/generate-digest` ¬∑ loading-state ¬∑ `router.refresh()` ved success","x":-860,"y":-670,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"lib-supabase","type":"text","text":"### `lib/supabase/`\n‚Ä¢ `server.ts` ‚Äî Server-side klient med cookies (@supabase/ssr)\n‚Ä¢ `client.ts` ‚Äî Browser-side klient til Client Components\nBegge bruger anon key fra `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`","x":-1260,"y":-510,"width":780,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"styling","type":"text","text":"### Styling\n`app/globals.css` ¬∑ Tailwind v4 + brand-tokens\n`--orange: #FF3700` ¬∑ `--offblack: #1A1A1A` ¬∑ `--gunmetal: #484848` ¬∑ `--bg: #F4F4F4`\nFont: DM Sans","x":-1260,"y":-350,"width":780,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"components-header","type":"text","text":"## Client Components","x":-1260,"y":-740,"width":780,"height":50},
		{"id":"edge-scrape","type":"text","text":"### Edge Func: scrape-articles\n`supabase/functions/scrape-articles/index.ts`\nDeno runtime\n\n**Flow:**\n1. L√¶s `sources` (active=true)\n2. `npm:rss-parser@3` parser hvert feed\n3. Dedup p√• URL\n4. Inds√¶t i `articles`\n5. Kald Gemini for summary + score","x":-360,"y":-940,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"page-saved","type":"text","text":"### `/saved` ‚Äî Gemte\n`app/saved/page.tsx`\nKr√¶ver login ¬∑ viser brugerens gemte artikler ¬∑ two-query pattern","x":-1260,"y":-890,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-digest","type":"text","text":"### `/digest` ‚Äî Ugentlig digest\n`app/digest/page.tsx`\nViser personlig AI-briefing ¬∑ knap til at generere","x":-860,"y":-890,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-feed","type":"text","text":"### `/` ‚Äî Feed\n`app/page.tsx`\nViser alle scraped artikler ¬∑ sorteret efter score ¬∑ gem-knap pr. artikel","x":-1260,"y":-1040,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"page-login","type":"text","text":"### `/login` ‚Äî Login\n`app/login/page.tsx`\nEmail + password via Supabase Auth\nManuel oprettelse i dashboard","x":-860,"y":-1040,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"api-route","type":"text","text":"### `/api/generate-digest` (Next.js Route)\n`app/api/generate-digest/route.ts`\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Auth-check via cookies\n2. Hent brugerens `user_saves` med JOIN p√• `articles` + `sources`\n3. Hent prompt-template fra `settings.digest_prompt`\n4. Erstat `{{week}}`, `{{year}}`, `{{article_count}}`, `{{source_count}}`, `{{article_list}}`\n5. Kald Gemini 2.5 Flash\n6. Parse Gemini's `KEY: value`-output ‚Üí `DigestContent`\n7. Match h√∏jdepunkter ‚Üí URLs via titel-fuzzy-match\n8. Upsert i `digests` med `user_id`","x":-360,"y":-1240,"width":770,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"user","type":"text","text":"### üë§ Bruger\n3 godkendte i Supabase Auth\nmieo@, thpn@, nimj@spring-cc.com","x":-1260,"y":-1240,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"vercel","type":"text","text":"### ‚ñ≤ Vercel\nHosting, SSR, env vars\nDeploy: `vercel --prod`","x":-860,"y":-1240,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"pages-header","type":"text","text":"## Routes (App Router ¬∑ Server Components)","x":-1260,"y":-1110,"width":780,"height":50},
		{"id":"sync-script","type":"text","text":"### `scripts/sync-prompt.js`\nNode.js CLI ¬∑ `node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\n\n**Flow:**\n1. L√¶ser `Digest System Prompt.md` fra Obsidian-vault\n2. Strip YAML frontmatter + prompt-noter\n3. Upsert til Supabase `settings`-tabel via REST API + service_role key\n\nKr√¶ver `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` i `.env.local`","x":-360,"y":-475,"width":770,"height":230,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cron","type":"text","text":"### pg_cron + pg_net (Supabase)\n‚Ä¢ `daglig-scraper` ‚Äî `0 4 * * *` (06:00 dansk tid) ‚Üí kalder scrape-articles\n‚Ä¢ `ugentlig-digest` ‚Äî `0 18 * * 0` _(s√∏ndag, deaktiveret)_\n\nKonfigureret i Supabase SQL Editor ‚Äî manuel ops√¶tning","x":-360,"y":-670,"width":770,"height":160,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"obsidian-prompt","type":"text","text":"### üìì Obsidian: Digest System Prompt.md\n`Claude_design/Prompts/Digest System Prompt.md`\n\n**Du redigerer her** ‚Äî strukturen, tonen, sektioner.\n\n**Variabler:**\n`{{week}}` `{{year}}` `{{article_count}}` `{{source_count}}` `{{article_list}}`\n\n**Output-format:** KEY: value (ikke JSON, mere robust)\n`INTRO:`, `TREND1_TITLE:`, `HIGHLIGHT1_TITLE:` osv.","x":-1260,"y":40,"width":500,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sync-flow","type":"text","text":"### ‚öôÔ∏è Sync-script\n`node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\n\n1. L√¶s noten\n2. Strip frontmatter\n3. Upsert til `settings.digest_prompt`\n\n_Kr√¶ver `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`_\n\n**Workflow:**\nObsidian ‚Üí script ‚Üí Supabase ‚Üí API ‚Üí Gemini\n_Ingen redeploy n√∏dvendig_","x":-700,"y":40,"width":480,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"settings-fetch","type":"text","text":"### üóÑÔ∏è settings.digest_prompt\nSupabase tabel-row\n\nHentet af `/api/generate-digest` ved hvert kald\n\n**Fallback:** hardkodet prompt i route.ts hvis tabel/row mangler","x":-160,"y":40,"width":480,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"gemini-call","type":"text","text":"### ü§ñ Gemini-kald\nVariabel-substitution ‚Üí POST til Gemini 2.5 Flash\n\n`temperature: 0.3`\n`maxOutputTokens: 2000`\n\n**Output parsing:**\n`parseKeyFormat()` ‚Üí `DigestContent`\n\nServer matcher h√∏jdepunkter ‚Üí URLs via titel-fuzzy-match","x":380,"y":40,"width":460,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"render","type":"text","text":"### üñ•Ô∏è Render\n`/digest`-siden\n\n‚Ä¢ Intro-paragraf\n‚Ä¢ Top 3 tendenser (nummererede cirkler)\n‚Ä¢ Ikke g√• glip af (klikbare links)\n‚Ä¢ Footer: genereret-dato + regenerer-knap","x":860,"y":40,"width":400,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"deploy-edge","type":"text","text":"### Edge Function deploy\n```\n./supabase-cli/supabase.exe \\\n  functions deploy <navn> \\\n  --project-ref mdevyscqhpaogvsblfyp\n```\nWindows: binary i `./supabase-cli/`\n_(ikke npm)_","x":490,"y":470,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"deploy-prompt","type":"text","text":"### Prompt-opdatering\n1. Rediger Obsidian-noten\n2. `node scripts/sync-prompt.js`\n3. N√¶ste digest-generering bruger ny prompt\n\n**Ingen redeploy n√∏dvendig** ‚Äî prompt l√¶ses ved hvert API-kald","x":890,"y":470,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"deploy-frontend","type":"text","text":"### Frontend deploy\n`git push origin main`\n‚Üí Vercel auto-deploy _(virker ikke altid)_\n\n**P√•lideligt:** `vercel --prod` fra terminal\n\n`spring-marketing-news.vercel.app`","x":90,"y":470,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"env-local","type":"text","text":"### `.env.local` (lokal ¬∑ gitignored)\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\nSUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY\nGEMINI_API_KEY\n```\nBruges af Next.js dev + sync-script","x":-1260,"y":470,"width":400,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"vercel-env","type":"text","text":"### Vercel Env Vars (production)\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\nGEMINI_API_KEY\n```\nSat via `vercel env add ... production`\nKr√¶ver redeploy ved √¶ndring","x":-840,"y":470,"width":400,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"supabase-secrets","type":"text","text":"### Supabase Secrets (Edge Functions)\n```\nGEMINI_API_KEY\nSUPABASE_URL\nSUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY\n```\nAuto-tilg√¶ngelige i Deno-runtime via `Deno.env.get()`","x":-420,"y":470,"width":400,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"tldr","type":"text","text":"## üöÄ TL;DR ‚Äî Vigtigste filer for ny udvikler\n\n| Fil | Form√•l |\n|---|---|\n| `app/page.tsx` | Feed-siden ‚Äî entry point for brugeren |\n| `app/api/generate-digest/route.ts` | Hjertet i digest-funktionen ‚Äî prompt + Gemini + parsing |\n| `supabase/functions/scrape-articles/index.ts` | Daglig RSS-scraper (k√∏rer via pg_cron) |\n| `lib/supabase/server.ts` | Auth-aware Supabase-klient til Server Components |\n| `scripts/sync-prompt.js` | Obsidian ‚Üí Supabase prompt-sync |\n| Obsidian-noten `Digest System Prompt.md` | Den faktiske prompt der styrer Gemini |\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Projektkontekst til Claude Code-sessioner |","x":-1300,"y":810,"width":2600,"height":280},
		{"id":"edge-digest","type":"text","text":"### Edge Func: generate-digest\n`supabase/functions/generate-digest/index.ts`\n_Legacy ‚Äî IKKE i brug_\n\nOprindeligt kaldt af pg_cron s√∏ndag aften som global digest. Erstattet af Next.js API-ruten der laver personligt digest pr. bruger.","x":30,"y":-935,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"rss","type":"text","text":"### üì° RSS-feeds\nTechCrunch AI ¬∑ VentureBeat AI ¬∑ HubSpot Marketing ¬∑ Moz Blog\nKonfigureret i `sources`-tabellen ‚Äî kan tilf√∏jes/deaktiveres direkte","x":555,"y":-370,"width":720,"height":130,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"gemini","type":"text","text":"### ü§ñ Gemini 2.5 Flash\nEndpoint: `v1/models/gemini-2.5-flash:generateContent`\n‚Ä¢ Scraping: dansk summary (3 bullets) + score 1-10\n‚Ä¢ Digest: KEY:-format ‚Üí server parser ‚Üí JSON i DB","x":560,"y":-520,"width":720,"height":130,"color":"2"},
